<form bindsubmit="formSubmit" class="form">
    <view class="form-section">
        <view class="form-title">订单信息</view>
        <view class="form-item">
            <label>消费金额</label>
            <view class="form-content">
                <input name="name" placeholder="请输入" value="{{money}}" bindinput="changeMoney"/>
            </view>
        </view>
        <view class="form-item" wx:hidden="{{money == ''}}">
            <label>使用积分</label>
            <view class="form-content">
                <van-stepper value="{{ point }}" step="5" min="0" max="{{maxPoint}}" disable-input />
            </view>
            <view>当前您的积分余额为10积分，本次最多可使用{{maxPoint}}积分。</view>
        </view>
    </view>

    <button form-type="submit" class="main-btn">提交</button>

    <view class="form-tips">
        <view>说明：</view>
        <view>1. 每100元可使用5积分抵扣5元，剩余金额请直接支付给商家。</view>
        <view>2. 订单完成后，每消费100元可得到3积分返还，可用于下次线下消费。</view>
    </view>
</form>